column5: Just finishing up the pontoon...  Cleaning up all the wiring/switches and connections and I have this hanging off the control. Going to look for a manual but thought I'd post here by chance someone might know.  Added image of control.  Any help appreciated, thx guys.
Thanks a ton!  Its a simple dash with no instruments so I guess they block the ends to avoid shorts etc. I'll see if I can find a replacement block as the rubber is long gone.
